Package: pitchxg
Title: Pitch xG
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ozayr", "Mohammed", , "ozayr.mohammed@nhs.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular Shiny app visualising shot data for the Womens
    EUROS 2025 using StatsBomb open data. Features interactive shot maps,
    player comparison tables, xG vs goals summaries, and explanatory
    captions for actionable insights.
